These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, cooking, camping, rock-climbing
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Hobby   | board-games | cooking | camping | rock-climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing-polo, golf, volleyball, surfing
1. the person who's sport is surfing-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Sport   | golf | surfing-polo | surfing | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, horror, sports, thriller
1. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person watching spy movies is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | sports | horror | thriller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, march, april, june
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Birthday   | march | february | june | april |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, bellflower, zinnia, marigold
1. the person who growsbegonia is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
3. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Flower   | marigold | zinnia | bellflower | begonia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-6::.
