.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, snowmobile, quad-bike, tram
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person driving the roller and the person driving the tram##2
3. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
4. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Transport   | tram | snowmobile | roller | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
