.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-20::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, sports, romance, martial-arts
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
2. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
4. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | sports | mystery | martial-arts |

 